# TCE CCSD — D2h symmetry, aufbau-corrected occupation
# The SAD guess converged to an aufbau-violating state:
#   MO 21 (b2u, Fe 4py, +0.049 Eh): wrongly occupied
#   MO 22 (b3u, Fe 4px, +0.120 Eh): SOMO (wrongly)
#   MO 23 (b3g, pi_g Fe-d/O-p, -0.164 Eh): wrongly virtual
#   MO 24 (b2g, pi_g Fe-d/O-p, -0.163 Eh): wrongly virtual
# Fix: swap 21<->23 and 22<->24 to put pi_g in occupied space.
# Freeze count: Fe=9, 2xO=2 -> 11 frozen cores total

scf
  rohf
  nopen 1
  maxiter 200
  vectors input feo2_anion_ccsd.movecs swap 21 23 swap 22 24 output feo2_anion_ccsd_swap.movecs
end

task scf energy

tce
  ccsd
  freeze 11
end

task tce energy
